{"tid":1862071,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫管局指無拿過懲教署生產的口罩　不清楚同事購買途徑","createTime":"2020-02-04T12:19:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T15:30:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d106ec4ab5448d07f3e3c379a5a6d723dba198df","tid":1862071,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1506637_1_20200204200540.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1506637_1_20200204200540.jpg&h=22d6ff7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥連續兩日表示，口罩要優先給醫護人員使用，但醫管局聯網服務總監楊諦岡說，醫管局沒有拿過任何懲教署生產的口罩，個別同事有沒有在其他途徑購買口罩，局方則不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥今早在行政會議前說，政府在世界各地、包括內地採購口罩不太成功，政府人員要「慳啲使」，騰出來給醫護人員用。<br />\n<br />\n她昨日亦在記者會說，懲教署生產的口罩供應不算大，她掌握了醫管局一天要消耗的口罩量，懲教署和科學園的生產線難以保證所有醫護人員持續有供應，政府沒有辦法在庫存不多的情況下，拿口罩出來派發給市民。<br />\n<br />\n本台向負責分發口罩的政府物流署查詢，署方在疫情爆發後曾將懲教署生產的口罩分發到哪些政府部門，以及分發數量多少，物流署暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506637-20200204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506637-20200204.htm&d=iVnpHeK512wFMD%2FK5G8l3eoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=11590001\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506637-20200204.htm&h=4f994f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506637-20200204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4048a2cc619aae141d608aa4a19c15e0864c9d67","tid":1862071,"uid":122,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.giphy.com/media/qK6SDQMeApQLm/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FqK6SDQMeApQLm%2Fsource.gif&h=69e26654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫管局   懲教署  林鄭"},{"pid":"290c2fcc4e5b2c405105e5a48792cab6b7cdb14c","tid":1862071,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":